Requirements
============

- Igor Pro 7
- Igor XOP Toolkit 7


Installation
============

- Copy the files in "LNLS_procedures" to the "Igor Procedures" folder located in the Igor Pro installation directory.
- Copy the files in "LNLS_helpfiles" to the "Igor Help Files" folder.
- Copy the files in "LNLS_extensions/xop" to the "Igor Extensions (64-bit)" folder.
